{"type": "article", "id": 13387, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2015-08-12T07:59:39Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 14387, "name": "秤"}, {"id": 1954, "name": "包装"}, {"id": 14388, "name": "减湿器"}, {"id": 14389, "name": "机顶盒"}, {"id": 3917, "name": "运动相机"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 33, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606061405105ualzgC6wVDI3BYZ.png", "contents": "\n\n<h3>\r\n\tGraava Sport Camera by Graava\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>近日，来自巴西的 Graava 团队推出了一款运动相机，除了和市面上大部分相机一样的拍摄功能以外，这款产品试图以后期编辑能力让自己从众多繁杂的运动相机中脱颖而出。他们通过分析所拍摄画面，选出相对高质量的内容，进行自动后期编辑并成片输出。用户可以自主选择视频的长度和背景音乐。利用 wifi 配对以后，内容也可以很方便地上传到社交网络上。<a href=\"https://getgraava.com/index.html\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看详细信息。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061355232aK3rfuy1NEOjsmi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67114914\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135523I0X2VN95CZrQsMtw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65158924\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135524wgAR68BX3CS7NMOP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57579462\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135525zMrwXH9kfBsE8UTC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59168704\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135525cGb0JjuNeT6F8oMC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.77872861\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135526c4Hxm8UPYRLOBjhZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57701711\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135526zn72xWIersuO6Rwc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.85696822\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tLe Cube by Fuseproject\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>最近，法国设计工作室 Fuseproject 推出了一款新型的数字网络机顶盒，名叫 “Le Cube”，听起来是不是有点儿像“乐视TV”？不过他们之间没有任何关系，Fuseproject 选择和法国一家电视台 Canal+ 合作，后者主要经营付费的卫星电视业务。机顶盒看起来非常酷炫，小小的方形盒子，全黑色的外形看上去很有质感，正面有“＋”符号。他们设计了 320×240 高像素小屏幕，除了日常的需求，还专门为老人和小孩设计了更为方便的交互界面，试图有效改善看电视这一行为体验。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135527lbEFQAuq5CHyXIt3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.60635697\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135528WkCIOrK0E75Rpj23.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.53789731\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135528cgimPSb0fd5WrOlL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.3801956\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135528qXLbQSdHoAWsjEO1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.37652812\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135529kOgxSb0RnuAmT6Wt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.37530562\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135529vLCqV6wB9O0siul5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.53422983\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606061355298gOKmbnx6RtT2epd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.37163814\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135530aUZvGfqHzbCeN0Xd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5391198\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135530IgCXOBHpUuJoW1bS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.60513447\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tNatural Dehumidifier by 250 Design\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>Google 一下“减湿器”，你估计能找到一大片结果，但相信大部分与你的室内装修格格不入。250 Design 最近推出了一款基本没什么“存在感”的减湿器，小巧的外形和鲜艳的颜色让它们看起来轻松活泼，可以随意放在家里任何一个角落，后面的设计可以让它挂在墙上不容易丢失，还可以放在需要减湿的抽屉里面。这是<a href=\"http://250.or.kr/portfolio/natural-dehumidifier/\" target=\"_blank\">购买链接</a>。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135531mZUfyqLu8BkaSGMW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61809524\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135531F1uxXPVfzps5aiUr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135532TUldH1RSVQ29yXfP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61238095\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135532UZyo3jBKl6dMkPsz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71047619\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606061355336cB1UnXakKtGC3rY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135534BzfWgq9wulEUK7yx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135534clbXuUEkQMKo3JPd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61142857\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135534KhuHoUEfFq36SQrO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tPull Pull Toilet by Haochen He\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>人有三急，但并不是全世界的洗手间都干净整洁，也并不是所有的洗手间都有分隔设计。针对这个问题，近日，设计师 Haochen He 给公共洗手间设计了一个隔绝帘子。它是一个圆柱形状的隔绝罩，当没有人使用时，可以悬挂在上方，方便洗手间的通风，当有人使用时，只需要拉下来，就可以隔成一个人的小空间。节约公共建设成本，同时保障个人隐私。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135535rljFwdotYigK57bP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62857143\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135535ekw18QLShORgcqud.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62857143\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tNew Package Design by Jessica Stoll\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>麦当劳乱七八糟的外带包装让设计师为他们操碎了心，最近，Jessica Stoll 设计了一款新的包装袋，新包装袋和现在的包装袋外观上差别不大，但它可以变身“立在桌上”，“拎在手里”，“坐在腿上”三种“姿势”，分别方便不同情形下用户的使用习惯，比如，当对折方形包装袋的边角，可以把下部变成尖尖的样子，插在缝隙里面，不容易倾倒。这是<a href=\"http://www.jessicastoll.com/\" target=\"_blank\">设计师的个人主页</a>，点击可以查看更多作品。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135535eZ46V8qxfc5EbJSi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74938875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135536GCS5WItNLnXMAQsZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68704156\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135536ovQqgeyfjOPTiaMC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75550122\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135537y6leaT1X5cvsCYuf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61369193\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061355374zkALD8Qq1ZRGgBt.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135538ZurYUoTBM0A3Jn1R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74327628\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135538tZJ6G4wRqb1uPOoe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72371638\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135539jOwxX5q9NaEsgebl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.53300733\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tThe Sinking Scale by Troy Turner\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>Troy Turner 设计了一款超级便携式的秤，它利用水受到压力变形的的特点，像一个暖水袋那样，装上水就可以轻松得到物体的重量。当不使用时，把水放干就可以把秤折起来收纳，外形简单时尚、轻松便携。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135539yUTYxbq2MnlvmNBa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62571429\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135539ElbhAQ5j2T30Lfon.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135540GTy6ri1H8adQYKDm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63047619\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135540JzL7KS8jWaRbrxCy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135541CF84taRAdE9kHcSV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.53333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135541H2bN1wOhv5xeflQs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70857143\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}